Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.10,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,最近雨多起来真苦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,下雨难道不挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:11.24,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,我们那最近天天下鲭鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.79,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,烧烤还是水煮都已经吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:18.74,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,青鱼挺好 喜欢不喜欢都不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,列车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.77,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.36,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,现在运行的只有池袋巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快好快好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去吧去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,合叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋站是终端式站台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶啥 终端式站台是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里就是池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,差点以为要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:09.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,终于到达池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,说起来终端式站台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,简而言之就是死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么了 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.90,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,发现入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,快速排除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 为什么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.90,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,攻击 上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香的气味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:37.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:38.45,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等等我
Comment: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.75,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,您睡醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.95,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,饭菜已经为您准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.64,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,今天的饭菜 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,鱼干还有蘑菇蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,加上苦瓜味增汤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.36,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,听起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.68,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,之前吃的也是苦瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.47,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,你喜欢苦瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,不 并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是葉香大人您讨厌它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.82,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,如果这样 今后就
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,只是有些奇妙的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.12,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,奇妙的感觉是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.63,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,这我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.54,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,明明从未吃过它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但却一股怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.13,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以才奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.04,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,这个是 哪里产的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.22,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去问问那个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们正在找一个叫中富葉香的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好大块头的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,注意礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 怎么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.16,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.60,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,还是 混太郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:45.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,挺可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是你的狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.46,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我曾经也养过一只
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.92,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是叫波奇的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.20,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你 叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是 它就是波奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都是从吾野来 接葉香你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是葉香 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.32,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你们 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道你还在生我的气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.45,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.21,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我为什么要生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.77,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,总感觉 是非常的难受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.16,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,胸口 像火一样灼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等一下葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.40,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你难道不记得我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是吧 失忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,难道和善治郎一样 被做了软绵绵手术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是一名喜欢天文学的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,在池袋每天都认真学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,学习很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.79,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,知晓未知也很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,世界会膨胀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,然后 将来的梦想是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.09,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,将来的 梦想是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.35,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.72,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,请您冷静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.15,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听我说葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.48,ZH-Main-Down,Vigilante,0,0,0,,她们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没想到这么快就找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,伤害公主的臭虫们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.57,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们和与葉香公主同席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,竟有如此老鼠屎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,总而言之是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.05,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,给我办了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,总之 打倒她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,看 这真的会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:28.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等 葉香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小命没了前功尽弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主 您有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.80,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.54,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,为什么这么重要的东西会放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.39,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你个鸟头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.06,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.20,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.89,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,都是因为她们公主才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,给我逮捕她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,绝对别放跑她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快点快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,为什么让她们逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:13.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我要把你们都告诉公主 全都变成凉粉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不好了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,考虑到按钮和公主的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.51,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是时候要好好考虑这两件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.22,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,明明我是非常警惕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,结果太天真了你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.36,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你说有什么吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你个大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,赶快把公主搬到其它地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你放跑的那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.86,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,很有可能是来抢夺公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这点事情都不能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.88,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,但是她本人很有可能并不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,她很喜欢那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.67,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这个那个的理由怎么那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你不是说公主就由你来守护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:56.71,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哪怕伤到脖子上的一根毛 也得给我好好记住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.63,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,准备转向架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,警备人员也要增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个难道不是真葉香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟挺奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那么奇怪的葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,竟然连我们都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怪确实挺奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想她确实是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,毕竟葉香也提到了波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对是葉香本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就是说 葉香的态度很气愤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,绝交水平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要是葉香 也会和自己绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这个是摩尔斯 摩斯密码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎和诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么要通过苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,很有可能根系藤蔓的延伸 与吾野建立起了联系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,从吾野到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,苦瓜最强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以说诚老师她讲了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,将苦瓜切开 截面为圆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 菜刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.12,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,测试测试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜里传来诚老师的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那作为日语来说确实挺可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,好吵啊 我这能听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,噢 能看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.07,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,看不见 声音专用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我们已经找到了让世界恢复原状的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是善治郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.66,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:35.66,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,虽然没有得到证实 但是假说信服度落在置信区间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.95,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,7G开通的起点应该有作为开关的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.84,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,而那个按钮 应该是开启状态的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.66,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是说 再按一次按钮的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G线路会被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.34,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,电波的影响就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.93,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是说很有可能回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这太简单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.87,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,但这却让我们忽略了它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我们太聚焦于应对个别现象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.16,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,根本没有时间去探求「根本原因」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.79,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这点确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那个按钮现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.11,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这点我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.90,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,但至少 假如我是庞太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.61,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,肯定会采取严密的警备措施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那些想要维持现状的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,还有想回到过去状态之人之间的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.50,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,按钮的存在将决定各自命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果有了新消息就再联络
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.88,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,通话过后的苦瓜可是非常好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.99,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.50,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,糟蹋粮食可不 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 变成平常的善治郎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:42.85,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,虽然最近的哈吧吧模式的时间已经延长到五分三十八秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这挺厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.15,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不 距离完全的程度还很远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这样延长下去就能恢复原状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.28,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,计算上需要九十四年以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.02,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,稍微考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,九十四年以后善治郎都去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是按钮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:07.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是说 存在类似「核足球」的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,总统发射核武器的必要工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一般由警备人员时刻提携着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这没危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是被偷盗了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,虽然这种情节小说和漫画多得让人发指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,现实却并未发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香变得如此冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有没有可能是按钮的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,既然按下按钮世界就会被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再按一次就能关掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,世界和葉香都有可能恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以才有那种不好的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟想到的只有这种可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,鼠目寸光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,人是会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是有一决胜负的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,先找到按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果真有决胜机会 一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好想法 赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又是小晶你的但但是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,找按钮没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,虽然挺好但要怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,找到它和得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是两个任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵尸的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是黑金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.66,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.48,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,从那之后附近车站的环境变化挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.96,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要继续这样僵尸全体 要么被霉菌腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.06,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要么被干燥得成粉末了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵尸竟然如此敏感啊 好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以你要和我们合作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.78,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我们有数量优势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.51,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们头脑 有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为啥是疑问句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.60,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,刚刚头脑担当诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,告诉我们 要是找到了终止7G的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说不定就能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,头脑担当是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是肌肉担当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.28,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那个按钮在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是能把世界变成这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必然拥有很强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说会很大的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 就好比酒桶那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,酒桶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.68,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.22,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,刚刚路过百货商店的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.98,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,诶 怎么了 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.62,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸竟然对大脑和花菜以外的东西感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.50,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,说明僵尸们也想变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.45,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这些僵尸们 很有可能是被「恢复」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.46,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,也就是对拥有力量的按钮 产生了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.65,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,而那是按钮的可能性就非常之高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 不是也可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个商城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我没去过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱想过精致的生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且咱最喜欢自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之前看到类似的广告就很向往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:47.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要去那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 难得来到了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,顺带去看看也问题不大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你就只是想去商城罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就是想购物罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大家都想去商城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,当然也要找按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,庞太郎那群人肯定会把它隐藏起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且感觉他好像挺威风凌凌的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.89,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,芃伊斯·庞太郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.98,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,听说是个乱逼逼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎也说了他很坏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还说他只考虑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再说了原本就和7G有关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是却不打算恢复原状 反而装得很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,应该是不想承担搞得乱七八糟的责任吧
