Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:15.69,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那么就在此站 始发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.45,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.78,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.12,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}这在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.58,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}没导引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:29.37,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}寻找 你的 旅途 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.42,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}哐当哐当 哐当哐当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.13,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}心情激动万分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.30,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}哐当哐当 哐当哐当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.05,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}吹响清阙的哨声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:45.39,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}就算世界脱轨了也问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:50.10,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我们能够一往无前 无论何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:54.11,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}下次会是什么样的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.48,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}等待着去开启呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:02.12,OP-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}来吧 永不停歇的旅途
Comment: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:09.97,JP-ED-Up,,0,0,0,,ed
